{"id": 2950, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你觉得什么样的状态才算真的“独处”？", "description": "有了手机和互联网之后，我们对“独处”的定义其实也有了点变化。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 8526, "comment_count": 30, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190516125223ka7ATMuHsVC3Rez8.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-19T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5798, "title": "现如今你觉得什么样的状态才算真的“独处”？", "content": "现如今你觉得什么样的状态才算真的“独处”？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 344027, "content": "断网/不用任何能联网的电子设备", "image": "img/option/option/20190516124726BcNR6xQEAgtD2fpy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344028, "content": "虽然连着网，但是不用社交媒体/不跟别人联系", "image": "img/option/option/20190516124625itbnT1fpB0v8LKar.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344029, "content": "只要是一个人呆在某个地方就算独处", "image": "img/option/option/20190516124609sQf0K8YxWF5MlNTD.GIF", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344038, "content": "只有随身物品，但有些可以跟自己对话（比如 Siri", "image": "img/option/option/20190516125029AnCacg2WJdvGzqMe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344033, "content": "只有随身物品，而且都是不能说话的那种", "image": "img/option/option/20190516124747SinGMHJzYCexpWNO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344030, "content": "没有任何随身物品，包括书和手机", "image": "img/option/option/2019051612534723WEXdamuP5Uy6D0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344035, "content": "虽然有很多人但都跟自己无关，比如地铁里", "image": "img/option/option/20190516125109IUylhax7njfYFRgB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344032, "content": "任何感觉到孤独的时刻都算", "image": "img/option/option/201905161255441vBCoQkhsKwbVdHZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 344046, "content": "都不算，我对独处有别的定义", "image": "img/option/option/201905161250035iACFoWm4LGd3Xuy.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}